<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/648015-at-the-very-end-of-the-book-bone-s">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[? At the very end of the book, Bone's mother abandons her and runs off with 'Daddy Glen'. What happens to Reese? Do they take her with them?<br /><br />? The scene where 'mama' goes out all 'tarted up' and comes back with a lot of groceries - was she prostituting on the side?<br /><br />? Why does her mother say that she'll never leave Bone as she's literally heading out the door to run away with Daddy Glen? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
