<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/10715409-bev"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1341522238i/10715409._UY100_CR7,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/10715409-bev">Bev</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    I believe that Daddy Glen was already sexually abusing Reese since she was showing signs of sexual activity. Children don't usually become sexually ac<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    I believe that Daddy Glen was already sexually abusing Reese since she was showing signs of sexual activity. Children don't usually become sexually active at such a young age. I just don't think that he took his rage out on Reese &amp; beat her like he did Bone. <br />I read an interview with Dorthy Allison where she said that her mother had Sugar Daddies when she was growing up. She stated that in her family they didn't believe in prostitution, but that they did think that every woman should use her womanly charms to get what they could. So I think that when she left all 'tarted up' she went to spend time with her Sugar Daddy. <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</span>
</div>
</div>
